<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@l;Fb1J}t/G*1Ml;Fb1J}t/G镜像l;Fb1J}t/GMirrorl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[*1M]镜像(Mirror): 雷分布将随机按照下述方式对称 [水平/垂直/对角/副对角/中心]对称<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Al;Fb1J}t/GAl;Fb1J}t/G无马步l;Fb1J}t/GAnti-Knightl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1A]无马步(A, Anti-Knight): 所有雷的马步位置不能有雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1B''l;Fb1J}t/G后平衡l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1B'']后平衡: 雷八方向上的总雷数均相等<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1B'l;Fb1J}t/G失衡l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1B']失衡: 每行每列雷数均不相同 1.每列雷数不相同 2.每行雷数不相同<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Bl;Fb1J}t/GBl;Fb1J}t/G平衡l;Fb1J}t/GBalancel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1B]平衡(B, Balance): (1) 每行雷数相等；(2) 每列雷数相等<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1C'l;Fb1J}t/GC'l;Fb1J}t/G八连通'l;Fb1J}t/GConnected'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1C']八连通'(C', Connected'): (1) 染色格的雷和 (2) 非染色格的雷各自八连通。染色区域和非染色区域至少有一个雷。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Cl;Fb1J}t/GCl;Fb1J}t/G八连通l;Fb1J}t/GConnectedl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1C]八连通(C, Connected): 雷区域八连通<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1C^l;Fb1J}t/GC^l;Fb1J}t/G树根l;Fb1J}t/GRootl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1C^]树根(C^, Root): 所有雷形成一个树根结构。该结构是由第一行的一个雷开始向下、左下、右下延伸而成的。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1D''l;Fb1J}t/GD''l;Fb1J}t/G矩形对角线l;Fb1J}t/GRectDiagl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1D'']矩形对角线(D'', RectDiag): 所有雷必须是1x1~1x4矩形或者长度2~4的对角线的一部分，这些形状之间不能互相接触（对角也不行）。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1D'l;Fb1J}t/GD'l;Fb1J}t/G战舰l;Fb1J}t/GBattleshipl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1D']战舰(D', Battleship): 每个雷区域为宽度为 1、长度不超过 4 的矩形，矩形不能对角相邻<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Dl;Fb1J}t/GDl;Fb1J}t/G对偶l;Fb1J}t/GDuall;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1D]对偶(D, Dual): 每个雷区域为 1x2 或 2x1 的矩形<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Hl;Fb1J}t/GHl;Fb1J}t/G横向l;Fb1J}t/GHorizontall;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1H]横向(H, Horizontal): 所有雷不能与其他雷横向相邻<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1H2Hl;Fb1J}t/G横横向向l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1H2H]横横向向: 在每一行中, 要么都没有横向相邻的雷，要么都至少有一个横向相邻的雷。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1HTl;Fb1J}t/GHTl;Fb1J}t/G纵向l;Fb1J}t/GVerticall;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1HT]纵向(HT, Vertical): 所有雷不能与其他雷纵向相邻<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1K1Cl;Fb1J}t/G马步八连通l;Fb1J}t/GKnight-Connectedl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1K1C]马步八连通(Knight-Connected): 雷区域马步连通<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1K1Sl;Fb1J}t/G马步蛇l;Fb1J}t/GKnight-Snakel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1K1S]马步蛇(Knight-Snake): 所有雷构成一条蛇。蛇是一条宽度为 1 的马步连通路径，不存在分叉、环、交叉<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1K2Fl;Fb1J}t/G马步花田l;Fb1J}t/GKnightFlowerl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1K2F]马步花田(KnightFlower): 染色格中的雷的八个马步位置内恰好有1个雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Ml;Fb1J}t/GMl;Fb1J}t/G多雷l;Fb1J}t/GMultiplel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1M]多雷(M, Multiple): 染色格的雷值*2(总雷数不受影响)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Nl;Fb1J}t/GNl;Fb1J}t/G负雷l;Fb1J}t/GNegativel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1N]负雷(N, Negative): 染色格中雷值取负<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Ol;Fb1J}t/GOl;Fb1J}t/G外部l;Fb1J}t/GOutsidel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1O]外部(O, Outside): 非雷区域四连通；每个雷区域以四连通连接到题版边界<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Ql;Fb1J}t/GQl;Fb1J}t/G无方l;Fb1J}t/GQuadl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1Q]无方(Q, Quad): 每个 2x2 范围内至少有一个雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Q~l;Fb1J}t/GQ~l;Fb1J}t/G雷无方l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1Q~]雷无方(Q~): 每个2x2区域内都至少有一个空格<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1S''l;Fb1J}t/GS''l;Fb1J}t/G传送门蛇l;Fb1J}t/GPortal Snakel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1S'']传送门蛇(S'', Portal Snake): 所有雷构成一条蛇。蛇是一条宽度为 1 的四连通路径，不存在分叉、环、交叉。题板的上下左右视为连通。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1S'l;Fb1J}t/G衔尾蛇l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1S']衔尾蛇: 所有雷构成一条蛇。蛇是一条宽度为 1 的四连通路径，不存在分叉、环、交叉, 蛇的头尾相连<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Sl;Fb1J}t/GSl;Fb1J}t/G蛇l;Fb1J}t/GSnakel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1S]蛇(S, Snake): 所有雷构成一条蛇。蛇是一条宽度为 1 的四连通路径，不存在分叉、环、交叉<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1S^l;Fb1J}t/G双头蛇l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1S^]双头蛇: 所有雷构成一条双头蛇。蛇是一条宽度为 1 的四连通路径，不存在环、交叉, 只存在一个分叉<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1S~l;Fb1J}t/GS~l;Fb1J}t/G蛇~l;Fb1J}t/GSnake~l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1S~]蛇~(S~, Snake~): 所有非雷构成若干条蛇。蛇是一条宽度为 1 的四连通路径，不存在分叉、环、交叉。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1T''l;Fb1J}t/G纯三连l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1T'']纯三连: 每个雷属于唯一的三连组(横/竖/斜)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1T'l;Fb1J}t/GT'l;Fb1J}t/G必三连l;Fb1J}t/GTriplet'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1T']必三连(T', Triplet'): 所有雷必须处于横、竖或斜方向的三连中<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Tl;Fb1J}t/GTl;Fb1J}t/G无三连l;Fb1J}t/GTripletl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1T]无三连(T, Triplet): 雷在横、竖、斜三个方向上不能构成三连<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1U'l;Fb1J}t/G一元'l;Fb1J}t/GUnary'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1U']一元'(Unary'): 所有雷不能与其他雷相邻或对角相邻<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Ul;Fb1J}t/GUl;Fb1J}t/G一元l;Fb1J}t/GUnaryl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1U]一元(U, Unary): 所有雷不能与其他雷相邻<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Bl;Fb1J}t/G桥l;Fb1J}t/GBridgel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2B]桥(Bridge): 所有雷构成若干组桥。桥是从题版左边界八连通连接（水平或斜角连接）到右边界，宽度为 1、长度与题版相等的一条路径<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2C'l;Fb1J}t/G连方'l;Fb1J}t/GConnectedl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2C']连方'(Connected): (1) 所有四连通雷区域为 1xn 或 nx1 的矩形；(2) 所有雷区域对角相邻<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Cl;Fb1J}t/G连方l;Fb1J}t/GConnectedl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2C]连方(Connected): (1) 所有四连通雷区域为矩形；(2) 所有雷区域对角相邻<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Fl;Fb1J}t/G花田l;Fb1J}t/GFlowerl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2F]花田(Flower): 染色格中的雷周围四格内恰好有1个雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2G'l;Fb1J}t/G三连块l;Fb1J}t/GGroup'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2G']三连块(Group'): 所有四连通雷区域的面积为3<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Gl;Fb1J}t/G四连块l;Fb1J}t/GGroupl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2G]四连块(Group): 所有四连通雷区域的面积为 4<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2G*l;Fb1J}t/G互异四连块l;Fb1J}t/GGroup*l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2G*]互异四连块(Group*): (1) 所有四连通雷区域的面积为 4 (2) 且它们形状不同（SZ 和 JL 型视为相同形状）<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2G^l;Fb1J}t/G互异连块l;Fb1J}t/GGroup^l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2G^]互异连块(Group^): 四连通雷区域的面积为 1 到 N 各一个。(N = 题板尺寸 - 1)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Hl;Fb1J}t/G横向l;Fb1J}t/GHorizontall;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2H]横向(Horizontal): 所有雷必须存在横向相邻的雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2HTl;Fb1J}t/G纵向l;Fb1J}t/GVerticall;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2HT]纵向(Vertical): 所有雷必须存在纵向相邻的雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2I1Cl;Fb1J}t/G残缺联通l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2I1C]残缺联通: 1.所有雷都必须根据副板指示的4对联通方向进行联通, 2.雷只有3种联通方法(上下/左右/对角/副对角)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2S'l;Fb1J}t/G分段'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2S']分段': 每行连续雷长度不同<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Sl;Fb1J}t/G分段l;Fb1J}t/GSegmentl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2S]分段(Segment): 每行有且仅有一组连续的雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Tl;Fb1J}t/G无三连l;Fb1J}t/GTripletl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2T]无三连(Triplet): (1) 雷在横竖两个方向上不能构成三连；(2) 非雷在横竖两个方向上不能构成三连<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Z'l;Fb1J}t/G零和'l;Fb1J}t/GZero-Sum'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2Z']零和'(Zero-Sum'): 每个4x4方块内的染色格和非染色格雷数相等<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Zl;Fb1J}t/G零和l;Fb1J}t/GZero-Suml;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2Z]零和(Zero-Sum): 每行的染色格与非染色格的雷数相等<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3C'l;Fb1J}t/G连通'l;Fb1J}t/GConnected'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3C']连通'(Connected'): 每个雷周围四格中恰有两个雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Cl;Fb1J}t/G连通l;Fb1J}t/GConnectedl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3C]连通(Connected): 每个雷周围八格中恰有两个雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3C^l;Fb1J}t/G连通^l;Fb1J}t/GConnected^l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3C^]连通^(Connected^): 每个雷周围八格中雷的数量为偶数（包括0）<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3El;Fb1J}t/G迭代l;Fb1J}t/G演化l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3E]迭代(演化): 每个3x1区域决定其中间下方1格是否为雷，演化被当前题板所有区域共享。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3H1Al;Fb1J}t/GHex1Al;Fb1J}t/G六角无马步l;Fb1J}t/GAnti-Knight-Hexl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3H1A]六角无马步(Hex1A, Anti-Knight-Hex): 六角无马步: 所有雷的UN UE NW ES DW DS的位置不能有雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3H1Ql;Fb1J}t/GHex1Ql;Fb1J}t/G六角无方l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3H1Q]六角无方(Hex1Q): 六角无方: 每个互相相邻的三个格必有一个雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Il;Fb1J}t/G反相l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3I]反相: 染色格中非雷视为雷，雷视为非雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Ll;Fb1J}t/G环l;Fb1J}t/GLoopl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3L]环(Loop): 所有雷构成一条环。环是一条宽度为 1 的八连通路径，不存在分叉和交叉，环的头尾相连<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3MAl;Fb1J}t/G三雷区l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3MA]三雷区: 题板正好有三个四连通雷区<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Ol;Fb1J}t/G横纵l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3O]横纵: 雷从四个方向中的任意一个连到题板外<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Pl;Fb1J}t/G游行l;Fb1J}t/GParadel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3P]游行(Parade): 可以通过骑士的移动方式，从某一个雷格开始，在只经过雷格的情况下，不重复且不遗漏地通过所有雷格<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Q'l;Fb1J}t/G无方l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3Q']无方: 任意四个雷不能作为一个横平竖直的矩形的顶点<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Ql;Fb1J}t/G正方形l;Fb1J}t/GSquarel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3Q]正方形(Square): 所有四连通的雷格区域组成实心正方形<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Rl;Fb1J}t/G引用l;Fb1J}t/GReferencel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3R]引用(Reference): 在第 X 行或第 X 列的格子的周围八格不能恰好有 X 个雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Tl;Fb1J}t/G无三连l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3T]无三连: 任意三个雷不能等距排布<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Wl;Fb1J}t/G风云l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3W]风云: 每行雷数不同，每列中最高的雷的高度不低于它左边一列的最高的雷的高度（特殊情况：如果某一列没有雷，那么它左边所有列都没有雷）。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Yl;Fb1J}t/G阴阳l;Fb1J}t/GYin-Yangl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3Y]阴阳(Yin-Yang): 所有雷四连通，所有非雷四连通，不存在2*2的雷或非雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@4Dl;Fb1J}t/G对角l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[4D]对角: 不同四连通雷区不可对角相邻<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@4Nl;Fb1J}t/G4Nl;Fb1J}t/G相邻l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[4N]相邻: 非雷周围四格必须有雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@4S''l;Fb1J}t/G阶梯''l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[4S'']阶梯'': 4S'' = 4S - 1 = 4S' + 1<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@4S'l;Fb1J}t/G阶梯'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[4S']阶梯': 雷值等于行号与列号之和, 但从0开始<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@4Sl;Fb1J}t/G阶梯l;Fb1J}t/GStaircasel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[4S]阶梯(Staircase): 所有雷被视为 X 个雷（X 为其的行列数之和）<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@4Ul;Fb1J}t/G4Ul;Fb1J}t/G晶胞l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[4U]晶胞: 第一行和最后一行雷分布相同，第一列和最后一列雷分布相同<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@A2l;Fb1J}t/GA2l;Fb1J}t/GA2 格是雷l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[A2]A2 格是雷: A2 格是雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@A2~l;Fb1J}t/GA2~l;Fb1J}t/GA2 格非雷l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[A2~]A2 格非雷: A2 格非雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@AAl;Fb1J}t/G吸引l;Fb1J}t/GAttractionl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[AA]吸引(Attraction): 场上不存在横竖方向上的雷—空—雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@AFl;Fb1J}t/GAFl;Fb1J}t/G下落l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[AF]下落: 雷区与题板下边缘四连通<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@AIl;Fb1J}t/G箭头l;Fb1J}t/GArrowl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[AI]箭头(Arrow): 生成固定八方向箭头图, 雷格需沿箭头可不重补漏遍历<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@ANDl;Fb1J}t/G与l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[AND]与: 你可以在后面输入多个左线来表示或关系(题板将按照A规则或B规则)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@AS'l;Fb1J}t/G自旋'l;Fb1J}t/GAutoSpin'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[AS']自旋'(AutoSpin'): 每个2x2区域内不能同时存在四种状态（染色雷、非染色雷、染色非雷、非染色非雷）。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@ASl;Fb1J}t/G自旋l;Fb1J}t/GSpinl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[AS]自旋(Spin): 每一行不能同时存在染色非雷格、非染色非雷格、染色雷格和非染色雷格<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@4Bl;Fb1J}t/G宾果l;Fb1J}t/GBingol;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[4B]宾果(Bingo): 每个格子被随机标记一个左线规则。当该格为雷时，完整题板必须满足该格的规则。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@BMl;Fb1J}t/G1B1Ml;Fb1J}t/G多雷平衡l;Fb1J}t/G多雷平衡(扫联会2)l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[BM]多雷平衡(1B1M, 多雷平衡(扫联会2)): 染色格被视为两个雷, 每行每列的“多雷雷值”相同。(线索格不一定是多雷规则) (1).列平衡, (2).行平衡<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@CTl;Fb1J}t/G仙人掌l;Fb1J}t/GCactusl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[CT]仙人掌(Cactus): 每个雷周围四格中恰有1或3个雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@DCl;Fb1J}t/G必对角l;Fb1J}t/GDiagonally Connectedl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[DC]必对角(Diagonally Connected): 每个雷对角相邻的四格中有至少一个雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@Gdl;Fb1J}t/GGDl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[Gd](GD): 1.每行值不大于上一行 2.每列值不大于左一列<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@GLl;Fb1J}t/G生命游戏l;Fb1J}t/GGame of Lifel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[GL]生命游戏(Game of Life): 每个雷周围八格中恰有2或3个雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@GMl;Fb1J}t/G棍木l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[GM]棍木: 棍木<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@GT2l;Fb1J}t/G所有四连通雷/非雷区域面积大于 2l;Fb1J}t/GGT2l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[GT2]所有四连通雷/非雷区域面积大于 2: 所有四连通雷/非雷区域面积大于 2<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@HYWl;Fb1J}t/G??l;Fb1J}t/G何意味l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[HYW]何意味(??): <==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@JBl;Fb1J}t/G格调l;Fb1J}t/GAdickl;Fb1J}t/GNTl;Fb1J}t/G2201963934l;Fb1J}t/G[JB]格调(Adick)[@Author=NT(2201963934)]: 每组恰好由 1 个非方形矩形和 2 个方形矩形组成；短边两端分别与两个方形矩形对角接触，且组间完全不接触<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@MBl;Fb1J}t/G平衡点l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[MB]平衡点: 所有雷的平均位置是整点<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@ORl;Fb1J}t/G或l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[OR]或: 你可以在后面输入多个左线来表示或关系(题板将按照A规则或B规则)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@PMl;Fb1J}t/G独一无二l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[PM]独一无二: 恰有一种方式从每行每列恰好选取一雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@PUZl;Fb1J}t/G拼图l;Fb1J}t/GPuzzlel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[PUZ]拼图(Puzzle): 所有四联通雷块可通过独立平移重排成一个轴对齐矩形<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@QTREEl;Fb1J}t/G四叉树l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[QTREE]四叉树: 将题版划分为四叉树，称所有节点均为雷的子树为大雷，大雷以外的节点不能有两个子节点同时为雷或大雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@RAWl;Fb1J}t/G原始雷值l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[RAW]原始雷值: 原始雷值<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@SCl;Fb1J}t/G甘蔗l;Fb1J}t/GSugar Canel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[SC]甘蔗(Sugar Cane): 每个雷周围至少有一个染色格, 且染色格不能为雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@SCREAMl;Fb1J}t/G尖叫l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[SCREAM]尖叫: 雷值等于其相邻四格雷数的阶乘<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@SETUl;Fb1J}t/G涩图l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[SETU]涩图: 禁止涩涩！<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@SETU^l;Fb1J}t/GSETUHl;Fb1J}t/G涩图融合l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[SETU^]涩图融合(SETUH): 参数链接(支持URL/文件路径)作为A图，与已生成题板图B融合并替换最终题板图<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@SMl;Fb1J}t/G???l;Fb1J}t/G神秘l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[SM]神秘(???): 这是一条会让男娘感到困惑的规则<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@TEST-L01l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[TEST-L01]: 所有雷组成两个四连通块，左下角与右上角必为雷且不联通<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@TEST-L02l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[TEST-L02]: 所有雷组成L形：雷总是组成L形，L形是宽度为1，拐弯一次的形状，L形可以斜角相邻但不能横竖相邻<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@TEST-L1l;Fb1J}t/GTEST-L1l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[TEST-L1]: 如果一个格子是雷，其水平对称格不是雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@TEST-L2l;Fb1J}t/GTEST-L2l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[TEST-L2]: 每一行各有一组连续的雷且数量各不相同<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@THEMEl;Fb1J}t/G主题l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[THEME]主题: 设置题板主题<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@U-ECHOl;Fb1J}t/G回声l;Fb1J}t/GNTl;Fb1J}t/G2201963934l;Fb1J}t/G[U-ECHO]回声[@Author=NT(2201963934)]: 回声：抛出参数。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@U-LLMl;Fb1J}t/G随机规则点子l;Fb1J}t/GNTl;Fb1J}t/G2201963934l;Fb1J}t/G[U-LLM]随机规则点子[@Author=NT(2201963934)]: 随机规则点子：随机抽词并由 LLM 联想生成规则描述后抛出。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@U-SAl;Fb1J}t/G反混合l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[U-SA]反混合: 对于一张透明图片，分别输入它在白底和黑底上混合颜色的结果，尝试还原原图。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@U-SETUl;Fb1J}t/G涩图l;Fb1J}t/GNTl;Fb1J}t/G2201963934l;Fb1J}t/G[U-SETU]涩图[@Author=NT(2201963934)]: 参数链接(支持URL/文件路径)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@U-YYl;Fb1J}t/G一言l;Fb1J}t/GNTl;Fb1J}t/G2201963934l;Fb1J}t/G[U-YY]一言[@Author=NT(2201963934)]: 一言：抛出一言（hitokoto.cn）。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@XSl;Fb1J}t/G分段l;Fb1J}t/GSegment Splitl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[XS]分段(Segment Split): 用副板表示行分段边界：无边界同值、两侧不同必为边界，边界数自底向上递增并满足行间继承<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Dl;Fb1J}t/G辞典l;Fb1J}t/GDictl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D]辞典(Dict): 所有雷从左到右，从上到下依次标号。线索表示周围八格的雷的标号之和<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Ul;Fb1J}t/G上上l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3U]上上: 每列最高的雷视为两个雷（总雷数不受其影响）<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3D1B'l;Fb1J}t/G平衡l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D1B']平衡: 所有平行面的总雷数均相等<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3D1Cl;Fb1J}t/G3DCl;Fb1J}t/G二十六连通l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D1C]二十六连通(3DC): 雷区域二十六连通<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3D1K1Sl;Fb1J}t/G三维马步蛇l;Fb1J}t/G3D-Knight-Snakel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D1K1S]三维马步蛇(3D-Knight-Snake): 所有雷构成一条蛇。马步蛇是一条马步联通路径，不存在分叉、环、交叉<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3D1Ql;Fb1J}t/G3DQl;Fb1J}t/G三维无方l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D1Q]三维无方(3DQ): 每个2x2x2区域内都至少有2个雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3D1Sl;Fb1J}t/G三维蛇l;Fb1J}t/G3D-Snakel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D1S]三维蛇(3D-Snake): 所有雷构成一条蛇。蛇是一条宽度为 1 的六连通路径，不存在分叉、环、交叉<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3D1T'l;Fb1J}t/G3DT'l;Fb1J}t/G三维必三连l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D1T']三维必三连(3DT'): 雷必然处在横竖对角构成三连<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3D1Tl;Fb1J}t/G无三连l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D1T]无三连: 雷不能在横竖对角构成三连<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3D1Ul;Fb1J}t/G3DUl;Fb1J}t/G三维一元l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D1U]三维一元(3DU): 所有雷不能与其他雷相邻<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3D2Fl;Fb1J}t/G三维花田l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D2F]三维花田: 染色格中的雷周围六格内恰好有1个雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3D2Tl;Fb1J}t/G无三连l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D2T]无三连: (1)雷不能在横竖上下向构成三连, (2)非雷不能在横竖上下向构成三连<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3DDl;Fb1J}t/G3D1Dl;Fb1J}t/G蛆l;Fb1J}t/G三维对偶l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3DD]蛆(3D1D, 三维对偶): 所有雷均形成1x2x1、2x1x1或1x1x2的三维矩形<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3DJl;Fb1J}t/G枣糕l;Fb1J}t/GJujubecakel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3DJ]枣糕(Jujubecake): 所有非雷格均形成1x2x1、2x1x1或1x1x2的三维矩形，即每个非雷格恰好有一个六连通相邻的非雷格(全是洞啊!!!)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3DWl;Fb1J}t/G海浪l;Fb1J}t/GWavel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3DW]海浪(Wave): 所有层的同一行列中有且只有一格有雷, 且所有雷的水平邻居中每一个的上下偏移一格以内的范围内必定有雷.
1. 对于任意x,y, 存在唯一z使得(x,y,z)有雷
2. 若(x0,y0,z0)有雷, 则{(x, y, z)| |x - x0| <= 1, |y - y0| <= 1, |z - z0| <= 1}中的雷格数为其2D邻格个数+1<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@F#l;Fb1J}t/G标签l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[F#]标签: 包含以下规则: [*3T], [3], [3F]<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3]: 雷指向的方向存在n个雷(不包括自己)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Fl;Fb1J}t/G不是Vl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3F]不是V: 雷线索表示附近八个格子内的非雷格数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Gl;Fb1J}t/G分组l;Fb1J}t/GGroupingl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3G]分组(Grouping): 相同数字的雷线索四连通<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@*3Tl;Fb1J}t/G雷三连l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[*3T]雷三连: 雷线索指示包含自身的雷三连数量。雷三连允许部分重合<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@CBl;Fb1J}t/GCCBl;Fb1J}t/G连击l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[CB]连击(CCB): 雷线索指示四方向的连击总值和，同方向相邻的n个雷连击值为1-n<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@FLl;Fb1J}t/G周长l;Fb1J}t/GPerimeterl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[FL]周长(Perimeter): 雷线索值表示所在雷区周长<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@#l;Fb1J}t/G标签l;Fb1J}t/GTagl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[#]标签(Tag): 线索会有不同的规则, 每个线索的规则会单独标出<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@SMVl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[SMV]: 对称雷值: 雷线索表示所在雷区中心对称范围内的雷数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@BTl;Fb1J}t/G副板共用l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[BT]副板共用: 不同副板规则的副板共用<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@MATEl;Fb1J}t/GMatel;Fb1J}t/Gmatel;Fb1J}t/G元l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[MATE]元(Mate, mate): 题板具有多块主板,多块主板的雷位置完全相同,但是题板具有不同的规则,规则将按照顺序标出<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@++l;Fb1J}t/G艹l;Fb1J}t/Gplusplusl;Fb1J}t/GNTl;Fb1J}t/G2201963934l;Fb1J}t/G[++]艹(plusplus)[@Author=NT(2201963934)]: 线索表示周围这些格子的雷数LL;LU;LD;L;RR;RU;RD;R<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@*1Fl;Fb1J}t/G翻转l;Fb1J}t/GFilpl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[*1F]翻转(Filp): 线索表示其以题板左上角到右下角直线为对称轴的镜像位置周围八格的雷数，不包括自身<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1E'l;Fb1J}t/GE'l;Fb1J}t/G视差l;Fb1J}t/GEyesight'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1E']视差(E', Eyesight'): 线索表示纵向和横向的视野之差，箭头指示视野更长的方向<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1El;Fb1J}t/GEl;Fb1J}t/G视野l;Fb1J}t/GEyesightl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1E]视野(E, Eyesight): 线索表示四方向上能看到的非雷格数量（包括自身），雷会阻挡视<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1EBl;Fb1J}t/G主教视野l;Fb1J}t/GBishop Eyesightl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1EB]主教视野(Bishop Eyesight): 线索表示斜向上能看到的非雷格数量（包括自身），雷会阻挡视线<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1EKl;Fb1J}t/GEKl;Fb1J}t/G马步视野l;Fb1J}t/GKnight Eyesightl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1EK]马步视野(EK, Knight Eyesight): 线索表示沿着马步方向能看到的非雷格数量（包括自身），雷会阻挡视线<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1EQl;Fb1J}t/G皇后视野l;Fb1J}t/GQueen Eyesightl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1EQ]皇后视野(Queen Eyesight): 线索表示八个方向上能看到的非雷格数量（包括自身），雷会阻挡视线<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1ESl;Fb1J}t/G螺旋视野l;Fb1J}t/GSpiral Eyesightl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1ES]螺旋视野(Spiral Eyesight): 该线索表示从当前格子向四周出发随后进行顺时针顺序旋转（类似卐字形）能看到的非雷格数量（包含自身）, 雷会阻挡视线。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Fl;Fb1J}t/G远视l;Fb1J}t/GFarsightl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1F]远视(Farsight): 线索表示朝向箭头方向到达雷或题板边缘时，垂直与箭头方向的连续非雷格数量<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Kl;Fb1J}t/GKl;Fb1J}t/G骑士l;Fb1J}t/GKnightl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1K]骑士(K, Knight): 线索表示马步位置 8 个格子中的总雷值<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1M'l;Fb1J}t/G多雷'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1M']多雷': 每个线索的多雷位置相对于线索固定 且位置全盘共享（不影响总雷数）<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1M1Nl;Fb1J}t/GMNl;Fb1J}t/G多雷 + 负雷l;Fb1J}t/GMultiple + Negativel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1M1N]多雷 + 负雷(MN, Multiple + Negative): <==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1MNXl;Fb1J}t/GMNXl;Fb1J}t/G多雷 + 负雷 + 十字l;Fb1J}t/GMultiple + Negative + Crossl;Fb1J}t/G1M1N1Xl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1MNX]多雷 + 负雷 + 十字(MNX, Multiple + Negative + Cross, 1M1N1X): <==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1M1Xl;Fb1J}t/GMXl;Fb1J}t/G多雷 + 十字l;Fb1J}t/GMultiple + Crossl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1M1X]多雷 + 十字(MX, Multiple + Cross): <==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1N1Xl;Fb1J}t/GNXl;Fb1J}t/G负雷 + 十字l;Fb1J}t/GNegative + Crossl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1N1X]负雷 + 十字(NX, Negative + Cross): <==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Pl;Fb1J}t/GPl;Fb1J}t/G分组l;Fb1J}t/GPartitionl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1P]分组(P, Partition): 线索表示 3x3 范围内连续雷的组数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@QLl;Fb1J}t/G1Q1Ll;Fb1J}t/G误差无方l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[QL]误差无方(1Q1L): 误差线索比真实值大1或小1，如果线索处在2*2非雷框内，则它是误差线索，反之则是真实值。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1W'l;Fb1J}t/GW'l;Fb1J}t/G最长数墙l;Fb1J}t/GLongest Walll;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1W']最长数墙(W', Longest Wall): 线索表示 3x3 范围内最长的连续雷的长度<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Wl;Fb1J}t/GWalll;Fb1J}t/G数墙l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1W]数墙(Wall): 线索表示 3x3 范围内每组连续雷的长度<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1X''l;Fb1J}t/GX''l;Fb1J}t/G双十字l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1X'']双十字(X''): 线索表示距离为1和距离为2√2区域的总雷数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1X'l;Fb1J}t/GX'l;Fb1J}t/G小十字l;Fb1J}t/GMini Crossl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1X']小十字(X', Mini Cross): 线索表示半径为 1 的十字范围内的雷数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1X+l;Fb1J}t/G城堡l;Fb1J}t/GCastlel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1X+]城堡(Castle): 线索数表示与其同行或同列的所有格子中的雷数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1X-l;Fb1J}t/G残缺十字l;Fb1J}t/GPawnl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1X-]残缺十字(Pawn): 线索表示朝向一个方向的两个格子中的雷数，线索会标注出方向<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Xl;Fb1J}t/G十字l;Fb1J}t/GCrossl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1X]十字(Cross): 线索表示半径为 2 的十字范围内的雷数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1X2Xl;Fb1J}t/G十字l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1X2X]十字: 线索代表半径为 2 的十字范围内中，染色和非染色格里的雷数(顺序不确定)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1X*l;Fb1J}t/G王后l;Fb1J}t/GQueenl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1X*]王后(Queen): 线索数表示斜向和横纵所有格子中的雷数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1XXl;Fb1J}t/G主教l;Fb1J}t/GBishopl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1XX]主教(Bishop): 线索数表示斜向所有格子中的雷数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1X^l;Fb1J}t/G菱形l;Fb1J}t/GRhombusl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1X^]菱形(Rhombus): 线索表示距离为 √2 和距离为 2 区域的总雷数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2A'l;Fb1J}t/G面积'l;Fb1J}t/GArea'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2A']面积'(Area'): 线索表示它所在的四连通非雷区的面积。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Al;Fb1J}t/G面积l;Fb1J}t/GAreal;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2A]面积(Area): 线索表示四方向相邻雷区域的面积之和<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2A1Pl;Fb1J}t/G面积 + 划分l;Fb1J}t/GArea + Partitionl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2A1P]面积 + 划分(Area + Partition): 线索表示四方向相邻雷区域的数量<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2A1W'l;Fb1J}t/G面积 + 最大数墙l;Fb1J}t/GArea + Largest Walll;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2A1W']面积 + 最大数墙(Area + Largest Wall): 线索表示四方向最大相邻雷区域的面积<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2A1Wl;Fb1J}t/G面积 + 数墙l;Fb1J}t/GArea + Walll;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2A1W]面积 + 数墙(Area + Wall): 线索表示四方向各相邻雷区域的面积<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2D''l;Fb1J}t/G偏移''l;Fb1J}t/GDeviation''l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2D'']偏移''(Deviation''): 线索表示以四方向偏移一格为中心的3x3区域内的雷数最多的区域的雷数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2D'l;Fb1J}t/G四向偏移l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2D']四向偏移: 线索表示四方向任意偏移一格为中心的3x3区域内的总雷数(全局统一)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Dl;Fb1J}t/G偏移l;Fb1J}t/GDeviationl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2D]偏移(Deviation): 线索表示以正上方一格为中心，3x3 范围内的雷数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2D^l;Fb1J}t/G偏移^l;Fb1J}t/GDeviation^l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2D^]偏移^(Deviation^): 线索表示 Nx3 范围内的雷数，N 为正上连续非雷格数量<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2E''l;Fb1J}t/G互指l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2E'']互指: 如果线索X周围有N个雷 则另一个题板的X=N的格子必定为雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`