t/G乘积l;Fb1J}t/GProductl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2P]乘积(Product): 线索表示距离最近的 2 个雷的距离之积<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Q'l;Fb1J}t/G章鱼l;Fb1J}t/GOctopusl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2Q']章鱼(Octopus): 线索表示八方向上最近的2格有雷的方向数量<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Ql;Fb1J}t/G皇后l;Fb1J}t/GQueenl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2Q]皇后(Queen): 线索表示八方向有雷的方向数量<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2X'l;Fb1J}t/G十字'l;Fb1J}t/GCross'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2X']十字'(Cross'): 线索表示 3x3 范围内染色格或非染色格的雷数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2Xl;Fb1J}t/G十字l;Fb1J}t/GCrossl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2X]十字(Cross): 线索表示 3x3 范围内染色格和非染色格的雷数（顺序不确定）<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@2*1Ll;Fb1J}t/G2倍误差l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[2*1L]2倍误差: 所有线索均比真实值大2或小2或者不变<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Al;Fb1J}t/G兰顿蚂蚁l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3A]兰顿蚂蚁: 数字表示兰顿蚂蚁从线索格出发直至走出题板外所移动的次数。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Bl;Fb1J}t/G二进l;Fb1J}t/GBinaryl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3B]二进(Binary): 无雷是0，有雷是1，线索代表每行（左起）和每列（上起）对应两个二进制数的按位异或值<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3H''l;Fb1J}t/G大三角l;Fb1J}t/GBig Trianglel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3H'']大三角(Big Triangle): 线索表示这些周围格子的雷数：周围八格 左左 右右，奇数列额外包括左左上 右右上；偶数列额外包括左左下 右右下<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3H'l;Fb1J}t/G小三角l;Fb1J}t/GTrianglel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3H']小三角(Triangle): 线索表示这些周围格子的雷数：左 右，奇数列额外包括上；偶数列额外包括下<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Hl;Fb1J}t/G六角l;Fb1J}t/GHexagonl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3H]六角(Hexagon): 线索表示六边形网格中与线索距离为1的格子中的雷数
线索表示正方形网格中这些周围格子的雷数：上 下 左 右，奇数列(B,D,F,...)额外包括左上 右上；偶数列(A,C,E,...)额外包括左下 右下<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Ml;Fb1J}t/G对映l;Fb1J}t/GMirrorl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3M]对映(Mirror): 线索表示周围八格组成四个正好相对的格子组有且仅有一个是雷的组数（题板外视为非雷）<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Nl;Fb1J}t/G范数l;Fb1J}t/GNorml;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3N]范数(Norm): 线索(a_p)表示距离自己lp范数最近的雷的lp范数大小为a。(p=0,1,2,00)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3Sl;Fb1J}t/G贝壳l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3S]贝壳: 线索代表相邻的8个格子中， 中间偏上5格范围和中间偏下5格范围里的雷数(顺序不确定)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@4Ol;Fb1J}t/G近视l;Fb1J}t/GMyopial;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[4O]近视(Myopia): 线索以上下左右箭头而非数字呈现，箭头指向四方向距离其最近的雷，同时存在多个雷距离最近时会显示全部箭头。四方向都不存在雷时显示零。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@4Ql;Fb1J}t/G方格l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[4Q]方格: 线索表示包含该格且包含雷的 2x2 区域数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@4V'l;Fb1J}t/G映射'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[4V']映射': 线索表示数字是三个题板中相同位置的其中某两个范围中心3*3区域的雷总数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@4Yl;Fb1J}t/G区域l;Fb1J}t/GAreal;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[4Y]区域(Area): 线索表示包含该格的最大无雷矩形区域的面积<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@6Vl;Fb1J}t/G经典扫雷(全标)l;Fb1J}t/GVanilla(Full Marking)l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[6V]经典扫雷(全标)(Vanilla(Full Marking)): 盘面上的数字线索标识周围八格的雷数。盘面上所有已给出的数字均已给出。其他格子不可能再出现已经给出的数字。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@AVGl;Fb1J}t/G平均l;Fb1J}t/GAveragel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[AVG]平均(Average): 四联通非雷格的线索值求平均<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@BIN'l;Fb1J}t/G二叉'l;Fb1J}t/GBinary'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[BIN']二叉'(Binary'): BIN':X;Y 表示线索为 X 或 Y 规则下的值<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@BINl;Fb1J}t/G二叉l;Fb1J}t/GBinaryl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[BIN]二叉(Binary): BIN:X;Y 表示线索为 X 与 Y 规则下的值（顺序不确定）<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@CPVl;Fb1J}t/G划分雷值l;Fb1J}t/GClue Partition Valuel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[CPV]划分雷值(Clue Partition Value): 线索格表示周围八格雷数, 且每个格子在其可见候选线索集合中必须唯一归属。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@CQl;Fb1J}t/G王后l;Fb1J}t/GChess-Queenl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[CQ]王后(Chess-Queen): 线索表示八方向上雷数总和<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@CSl;Fb1J}t/G罗盘l;Fb1J}t/GCompassl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[CS]罗盘(Compass): 线索表示四方向各相邻雷区域中，在所示方向上比线索本身更远的单元格数量。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@4D'l;Fb1J}t/G对映合并l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[4D']对映合并: 每个数字标明周围八格内雷的数量。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@MCl;Fb1J}t/G染色格合并l;Fb1J}t/GMine-Combinationl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[MC]染色格合并(Mine-Combination): 线索表示周围八格的雷数，染色格中如有雷就同一算为一雷（剩余雷数不受影响）<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@PFl;Fb1J}t/G素因子l;Fb1J}t/GPrime Factorl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[PF]素因子(Prime Factor): 除0和1外的线索显示真实值的最大素因子<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@?l;Fb1J}t/G问号l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[?]问号: 线索表示该格是一个非雷<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@Rule-011l;Fb1J}t/G没想好l;Fb1J}t/GτBl;Fb1J}t/GRULE-011l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[Rule-011]没想好(τB, RULE-011): 线索表示周围八格中周围四格没有雷的雷数。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@Rule-012l;Fb1J}t/G没想好l;Fb1J}t/GτCl;Fb1J}t/GRULE-012l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[Rule-012]没想好(τC, RULE-012): 每个雷的雷值等于它周围八格（包括自身）的总雷数，总雷数不受此规则影响。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@Rule-013l;Fb1J}t/G没想好l;Fb1J}t/GτDl;Fb1J}t/GRULE-013l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[Rule-013]没想好(τD, RULE-013): 如果一个雷的周围八格有四个及以上的雷，那么这个雷的雷值是0，总雷数不受此规则影响。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@#l;Fb1J}t/G标签l;Fb1J}t/GTagl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[#]标签(Tag): 线索会有不同的规则, 每个线索的规则会单独标出<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@Spl;Fb1J}t/G跨越l;Fb1J}t/GSpanl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[Sp]跨越(Span): 线索表示能连接周围八格内所有雷的最短连续路径长度。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@TVl;Fb1J}t/GTapaViewl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[TV](TapaView): 线索表示四方向上能看到的雷格数量，空格会阻挡视线<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@UPl;Fb1J}t/G唯一路径l;Fb1J}t/GUnique Pathl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[UP]唯一路径(Unique Path): 线索格表示从这个格开始只能往右或下走，到达右下角的方法数。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@V''l;Fb1J}t/G雷绝对值l;Fb1J}t/GAbsolutel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[V'']雷绝对值(Absolute): 每个数字标明周围八格内雷值之和之绝对值<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@V'l;Fb1J}t/G雷值l;Fb1J}t/GValuel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[V']雷值(Value): 每个数字标明周围八格内雷值之和<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@Vl;Fb1J}t/G标准扫雷l;Fb1J}t/GVanlial;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[V]标准扫雷(Vanlia): 每个数字标明周围八格内雷的数量。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1Ll;Fb1J}t/GLl;Fb1J}t/G误差l;Fb1J}t/GLiarl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1L]误差(L, Liar): 所有线索均比真实值大1或小1<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1L1E'l;Fb1J}t/GLE'l;Fb1J}t/G误差 + 视差l;Fb1J}t/GLiar + Eyesight'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1L1E']误差 + 视差(LE', Liar + Eyesight'): <==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1L1El;Fb1J}t/GLEl;Fb1J}t/G误差 + 视野l;Fb1J}t/GLiar + Eyesightl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1L1E]误差 + 视野(LE, Liar + Eyesight): <==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1L1Kl;Fb1J}t/GLKl;Fb1J}t/G误差 + 骑士l;Fb1J}t/GLiar + Knightl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1L1K]误差 + 骑士(LK, Liar + Knight): <==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1L1Ll;Fb1J}t/GLLl;Fb1J}t/G误差 + 误差l;Fb1J}t/GLiar + Liarl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1L1L]误差 + 误差(LL, Liar + Liar): <==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1L1Ml;Fb1J}t/GLMl;Fb1J}t/G误差 + 多雷l;Fb1J}t/GLiar + Multiplel;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1L1M]误差 + 多雷(LM, Liar + Multiple): <==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1LMNl;Fb1J}t/GLMNl;Fb1J}t/G误差 + 多雷 + 负雷l;Fb1J}t/GLiar + Multiple + Negativel;Fb1J}t/G1L1M1Nl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1LMN]误差 + 多雷 + 负雷(LMN, Liar + Multiple + Negative, 1L1M1N): <==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1LMNXl;Fb1J}t/GLMNXl;Fb1J}t/G误差 + 多雷 + 负雷 + 十字l;Fb1J}t/GLiar + Multiple + Negative + Crossl;Fb1J}t/G1L1M1N1Xl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1LMNX]误差 + 多雷 + 负雷 + 十字(LMNX, Liar +