l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3DV]3D标准扫雷: 每个数字标明周围26格内雷的数量。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3DKl;Fb1J}t/G3D1Kl;Fb1J}t/G3D标准扫雷l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3DK]3D标准扫雷(3D1K): 每个数字标明周围26格内雷的数量。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3D1X'l;Fb1J}t/G三维十字'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D1X']三维十字': 线索表示半径为 1 的十字范围内的雷数(上下左右前后)<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@3D1Xl;Fb1J}t/G三维十字l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[3D1X]三维十字: 线索表示(上下左右前后)2格的十字范围内的雷数<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@0L#l;Fb1J}t/G标签l;Fb1J}t/GTagl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[0L#]标签(Tag): 包含以下规则: [1L], [1L1L], [1L1N], [1L1X], [1L1P], [1L1X'], [1L1K], [1L1W'], [1L1E'], [1L2D], [1L2M], [1L2X']。线索值只有零。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@0#l;Fb1J}t/G标签l;Fb1J}t/GTagl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[0#]标签(Tag): 包含以下规则: [1L], [1N], [1E'], [1M1N], [1N1X], [2M], [2X']。线索值只有零。<==en_o[4\)dv%5`R&;K+7EYI)c]]8`t^1wGWTcW[YGN**]A'@1L1#'l;Fb1J}t/G误差 + 标签'l;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/Gl;Fb1J}t/G[1L1#']误差 + 标签': 包含以下规则: [1L], [1L1M], [1L1L], [1L1N], [1L1W], [1L1N], [1L1X], [1L1P], [1L1E], [1L1X'], [1L1K], [1L1W'], [1L1E'], [1LMN], [1LMX], [1LNX]
